│   │   ├── presentation/    # UI and widgets
│   │   ├── domain/          # Business logic (use cases, repositories)
│   │   ├── data/            # Data layer (models, repositories implementation)
│   ├── scan/                # Scan rice disease feature
│   │   ├── presentation/
